1. The Benefits and challenges of the MVC 
(1) benefits
Easy to mantian. When you change codes in Views, you don't need to change the code in control.
Easy to reuse. When you want to expand the language of system, you can easily reuse the origanl code.

(2) challenges
If you just want to implement a small project, MVC might make it more complex than it should have.


2. What makes a good GUI?
(1) It should be user friendy.
(2) The lables and buttons should have meaningful name.
(2) It should provide the correct feedback when user give input.
